    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>In their hunger for immortality humanity fought &quot;Death the Aeon&quot; but the battle was lost.. their hope was shattered.. and a curse was cast upon them..</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/909dd719e779b7038ea6b4467d16633d.avif?t=1770998893\" width=640 height=613 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A tale of Struggle  </strong><br><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.poster.avif?t=1770998893\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.webm?t=1770998893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/fee8f2ab2944546c90248c2a7b610844.mp4?t=1770998893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With only 7 days left, humanity's only hope is hidden in Guardiah tower but a world now in turmoil will trust hope ? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start your journey to Save humanity from the grasp of Death and experience the beginning of the the Epic Saga. </strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Demo </strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.poster.avif?t=1770998893\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.webm?t=1770998893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108270/extras/968d106c2d9b1d38d86db1cd9278d2e2.mp4?t=1770998893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A lengthy demo</strong> to introduce you to the story and let you taste the gameplay playing with five of the main characters. The demo is always updated with the latest features and <u><strong>your progress will be loaded in the full version. </strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><strong>Meet the protagonists, &quot;Enter <u>Guardiah Tower</u>,   escape the <u>Old Forest</u>,   visit the <u>Forbidden Library</u>   and sneak around the town of <u>Osha</u>&quot; .  </strong>  <br>   <br><strong>And once you are ready for more jump in the <u>full adventure</u> and continue from where you left to enjoy a <u>story full of lore</u>, <u>ten bad ending</u>, <u>mystery</u> and <u>humor</u>.</strong>           <br>       <br>       <br>       <br>       <br>       <br>       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
